LEA-001	Leave Application	Leave Application Creation & Basic Details	Create Leave Application with mandatory fields only (Employee, Leave Type, From Date, To Date)
LEA-002	Leave Application	Leave Application Creation & Basic Details	Create Leave Application with all basic fields (Employee, Leave Type, Dates, Company, Approver)
LEA-003	Leave Application	Series & Auto-generation	Series field is auto-generated in format HR-LAP-.YYYY.-
LEA-004	Leave Application	Series & Auto-generation	Series field cannot be manually edited
LEA-005	Leave Application	Series & Auto-generation	Unique Series is generated for each leave application
LEA-006	Leave Application	Employee Selection	Valid employee can be selected in Employee field
LEA-007	Leave Application	Employee Selection	Invalid/non-existent employee is rejected
LEA-008	Leave Application	Employee Selection	Employee field is mandatory and cannot be left blank
LEA-009	Leave Application	Leave Type Selection	Valid leave type can be selected from dropdown
LEA-010	Leave Application	Leave Type Selection	Leave Type field is mandatory and cannot be left blank
LEA-011	Leave Application	Leave Type Selection	Leave Type displays all available options (Annual, Sick, Personal, etc.)
LEA-012	Leave Application	Leave Type Selection	Employee's leave balance is checked for selected leave type
LEA-013	Leave Application	Company Details	Valid company is selected and displayed
LEA-014	Leave Application	Company Details	Company field is mandatory
LEA-015	Leave Application	Company Details	Company auto-populates based on employee's assigned company
LEA-016	Leave Application	Date Range	From Date is mandatory and cannot be left blank
LEA-017	Leave Application	Date Range	To Date is mandatory and cannot be left blank
LEA-018	Leave Application	Date Range	From Date cannot be after To Date
LEA-019	Leave Application	Date Range	From Date cannot be in the past
LEA-020	Leave Application	Date Range	To Date cannot be before From Date
LEA-021	Leave Application	Date Range	Invalid date format is rejected
LEA-022	Leave Application	Date Range	Leave duration is calculated correctly (From Date to To Date)
LEA-023	Leave Application	Half Day Leave	Half Day checkbox can be checked
LEA-024	Leave Application	Half Day Leave	Half Day checkbox can be unchecked
LEA-025	Leave Application	Half Day Leave	Half Day with single date (From Date = To Date) is valid
LEA-026	Leave Application	Half Day Leave	Half Day with date range is rejected
LEA-027	Leave Application	Half Day Leave	Half Day reduces leave balance by 0.5 days
LEA-028	Leave Application	Half Day Leave	Full day reduces leave balance by 1 day
LEA-029	Leave Application	Reason	Reason field is optional
LEA-030	Leave Application	Reason	Reason field accepts text input
LEA-031	Leave Application	Reason	Reason field accepts special characters
LEA-032	Leave Application	Leave Approver	Valid leave approver can be selected
LEA-033	Leave Application	Leave Approver	Invalid approver is rejected
LEA-034	Leave Application	Leave Approver	Leave Approver field is mandatory and cannot be left blank
LEA-035	Leave Application	Leave Approver	Leave Approver must have approval authority for the employee
LEA-036	Leave Application	Posting Date	Posting Date is auto-populated with current date
LEA-037	Leave Application	Posting Date	Posting Date cannot be manually changed
LEA-038	Leave Application	Posting Date	Posting Date is recorded accurately on submission
LEA-039	Leave Application	Leave Balance	Leave balance is displayed for selected leave type
LEA-040	Leave Application	Leave Balance	Leave balance decreases after leave application is approved
LEA-041	Leave Application	Leave Balance	Leave balance is restored after leave is cancelled
LEA-042	Leave Application	Leave Balance	Leave application is rejected if balance is insufficient
LEA-043	Leave Application	Leave Balance	Leave balance updates are reflected in real-time
LEA-044	Leave Application	Status & Workflow	Status defaults to Open on creation
LEA-045	Leave Application	Status & Workflow	Status changes to Approved after approval
LEA-046	Leave Application	Status & Workflow	Status changes to Rejected after rejection
LEA-047	Leave Application	Status & Workflow	Cancelled leave application shows Cancelled status
LEA-048	Leave Application	Status & Workflow	Only authorised user can approve leave application
LEA-049	Leave Application	Data Validation	Leave Application cannot be saved without Employee
LEA-050	Leave Application	Data Validation	Leave Application cannot be saved without Leave Type
LEA-051	Leave Application	Data Validation	Leave Application cannot be saved without From Date
LEA-052	Leave Application	Data Validation	Leave Application cannot be saved without To Date
LEA-053	Leave Application	Data Validation	Leave Application cannot be submitted with From Date after To Date
LEA-054	Leave Application	Editing & Updates	Edit Leave Type on existing leave application
LEA-055	Leave Application	Editing & Updates	Edit date range on existing leave application
LEA-056	Leave Application	Editing & Updates	Edit reason on existing leave application
LEA-057	Leave Application	Editing & Updates	Edit leave approver before submission
LEA-058	Leave Application	Editing & Updates	Edit is restricted after leave is approved
LEA-059	Leave Application	Form Actions	Save Leave Application successfully
LEA-060	Leave Application	Form Actions	Submit Leave Application successfully
LEA-061	Leave Application	Form Actions	Form shows "Not Saved" status before save
LEA-062	Leave Application	Form Actions	Form shows "Saved" status after successful save
LEA-063	Leave Application	Form Actions	Duplicate existing Leave Application
LEA-064	Leave Application	Form Actions	Cancel submitted Leave Application
LEA-065	Leave Application	Form Actions	Delete Draft Leave Application